1
00:01:29,570 --> 00:01:33,000
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:36,170
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,759
Master.

4
00:01:42,610 --> 00:01:44,200
Why did you break in here without consent?

5
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,720
Didn't I tell you to wait for me
and take care of your mother?

6
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,120
I couldn't wait anymore.

7
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:50,289
My mother's condition suddenly worsened.

8
00:01:50,289 --> 00:01:52,310
The doctor asked me
to fetch the antidote soon,

9
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:54,310
or she might not survive this month.

10
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,560
Only those on death row
would be brought to Lingya Tower.

11
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,979
How did you sneak in here?

12
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,460
The new top scholar was beheaded
and his body was discarded out of town.

13
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:05,010
The killer hasn't been caught yet.

14
00:02:05,010 --> 00:02:07,260
I just turned myself in to the authorities

15
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,250
and took the fall.

16
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:08,870
Ridiculous!

17
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:09,979
You didn't commit any offense,

18
00:02:09,979 --> 00:02:12,200
but everyone else in this tower
is a vicious criminal.

19
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,200
-Do you know how dangerous...
-I know.

20
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,280
You told me about it.

21
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:15,880
Once in Lingya Tower,

22
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,880
there are slim chances of survival.

23
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,790
I'll try to find the antidote
as soon as possible.

24
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,720
I'll also think of a way
to get you out of here.

25
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,050
But I'm already in here.

26
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,410
It's the eighth drum beat.

27
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:32,270
The incense is almost burned out.

28
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,240
You have to go now.

29
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,620
The exit is right in that alley.

30
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:35,480
Insert the key,

31
00:02:35,490 --> 00:02:36,670
and the door will open.

32
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,530
Then you'll win this death match.

33
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,990
What are you waiting for?

34
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,860
Kill her now.

35
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,640
Do it!

36
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,140
Step back!

37
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:40,960
Don't come near me!

38
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:43,960
Watch out!

39
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,720
Why not continue?

40
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,650
I only brought one dart.

41
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:54,110
I'll have to pull it out
if I am to use it again.

42
00:04:24,890 --> 00:04:25,530
Hold this.

43
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,020
Take it.

44
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:35,090
I, Dao, never use swords.

45
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,500
They're clunky and of no help,

46
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,720
just like men.

47
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:44,020
Thanks for your help.

48
00:04:47,210 --> 00:04:48,870
I didn't come here to help you.

49
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,380
The only reason I'm here is that this girl

50
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:52,980
took the key to the exit door.

51
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,580
Yanzhi,

52
00:04:54,610 --> 00:04:56,390
I was spotted by them when I just found

53
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,550
the key in the alley.

54
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,360
This is the key?

55
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:58,880
Yes.

56
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,300
It's the ninth drum beat.

57
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:04,210
How could you do that?

58
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,900
I thought you were on our side.

59
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,300
Don't you know the rules?

60
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,800
Only one of us

61
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,330
can get out of here alive.

62
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:32,159
It's true that only one can live,

63
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:35,090
but obviously it's not the person
who opens the door.

64
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,060
-Open up!
-Open the door!

65
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:43,960
-Open the door!
-Open up!

66
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,960
Open the door now!

67
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,680
The bottom-level death match is over.

68
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:59,360
You've passed the challenge.

69
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:17,780
We've made it through.

70
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,500
This is great, Yanzhi.

71
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,220
Let's go.

72
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,800
I finally made a right bet!

73
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,760
Three survivors.

74
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,290
Isn't it against the rules?

75
00:06:37,409 --> 00:06:38,260
Rules?

76
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:39,880
Since when are there so many rules
in Lingya Tower?

77
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,200
Now that all three girls
have made it through,

78
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,260
the result should be deemed as valid!

79
00:06:43,530 --> 00:06:44,800
In that case,

80
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,880
how do we settle the bets?

81
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:48,240
Each of the two of you
bet right on one person.

82
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,500
So you can split the prize money equally.

83
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:54,810
Split it equally?

84
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:56,110
Of course you're happy now.

85
00:06:56,110 --> 00:06:57,790
If these girls fight again,

86
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,040
the one named Jiang Man who you bet on

87
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,909
will definitely lose!

88
00:06:59,909 --> 00:07:01,150
What do you want then?

89
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:02,760
Are we going to make them fight
another round?

90
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,800
Yes, absolutely!

91
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,560
For what reason?

92
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,840
I already made the right bet.

93
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:06,720
So did I!

94
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,720
Harmony brings wealth.

95
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,880
-Only one can be the winner.
-Harmony brings wealth.

96
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,800
I have a proposal.

97
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,830
Those girls

98
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:14,380
are all beautiful and gorgeous.

99
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:17,080
If the two distinguished guests of you
don't mind,

100
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,720
why not go have a good time with them?

101
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,140
Won't that be wonderful?

102
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,520
Then send that girl

103
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,210
with strong combat skills to me.

104
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:25,000
Wujiu.

105
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,120
Yes.

106
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,200
You heard what we said, didn't you?

107
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,400
Go make arrangements now.

108
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:29,940
Yes.

109
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:34,110
What's this place?

110
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,000
Yanzhi,

111
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,570
what does this mean?

112
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,780
What's this smell?

113
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,010
Here I come.

114
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:30,830
You shouldn't have targeted these girls.

115
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,299
[First Meeting]

116
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:42,470
There's a rabbit.

117
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,270
You...

118
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,020
You...

